    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Bb_Cave40">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="bold">40</hi>號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>該窟位於南坡<foreign xml:lang="en">B</foreign>區。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁方向：350°。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>疑為方形窟。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>窟底高於現在平緩向東下降的小徑約2.5米，低於相鄰的<hi rend="bold">39</hi>號窟窟底約30釐米。</item>
                            <item>窟口前部寬：220釐米。</item>
                            <item>進深：45釐米。</item>
                            <item>高度：約80釐米。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>石窟未完工。僅開鑿出前部窟口的下半部，但未及深鑿。</p>
                        <figure rend="page" n="figure" xml:id="cave_40_DSC_0108.JPG">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">
                                <hi rend="bold">40</hi>號窟，僅在石壁鑿出一部分；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Cave <hi rend="bold">40</hi> was cut only partly from the rock; 
                            photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="cave_40_DSC_0108.JPG"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head type="cave">Cave <hi rend="bold">40</hi>
                </head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Southern slope, section B </item>
                            <item>Direction: wall f 350˚</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Intended box shape</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Height above present walkway, which slowly declines towards the east: 2.5 meters, ca. 30 cm lower than the floor of neighboring cave <hi rend="bold">39</hi>.</item>
                            <item>Width of opening at front: 220 cm</item>
                            <item>Depth: 45 cm</item>
                            <item>Height: ca. 80 cm</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>Unfinished cave. Only the lower
                        part of the front opening was cut into the rock, but not very deep.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
